    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Students on <strong>pre-registration healthcare</strong> programmes should check their programme handbook to clarify regulations relating to progression. There may be limits on the number of credits that can be carried to the next level of studies.</p>
<p>For most <strong>pre-registration healthcare</strong> programmes it is not possible to condone a module (regulation 17.4). Details will be provided in the programme handbook.</p>
<p> </p>]]></Value>
